{"tid":2231347,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個幫人揸機影相嘅經歷","createTime":"2020-10-05T14:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T14:57:45.000Z","uid":205508,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a13969c149c5f4ad7c604a6f935787e7d5c9cd0","tid":2231347,"uid":205508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"話說幾年前，小弟去意大利威尼斯旅行<br />\n<br />\n咁行行下有個鬼佬問我可唔可以幫佢地一家三口影相<br />\n咁助人為快樂之本嘛 緊係幫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老豆老母中間拖住個仔<br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oc3GnhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foc3GnhV.png&h=664b342f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果我一個唔小心 miss左佢個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjWD8Yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjWD8Yf.png&h=c36a24d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我影完之後突然之間醒起 仆街 唔記得影個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拿拿臨補飛影多張比返部機人地 即刻急急腳走<br />\n<br />\n行都冇幾遠 見到個家人望住部機 擰晒頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後仲要搵個第二個人 喺同一個位置 影同一張相 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自此之後 我都唔敢再幫人影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2f3dcfd6429e4730f45a235a1d649b72c9003e","tid":2231347,"uid":140335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"同老婆去睇聖誕燈飾<br />\n之後有對情侶叫我幫佢哋影相<br />\n我話 好啊 冇問題 但等陣要交換你都幫我哋影喎<br />\n<br />\n之後幫佢哋影左幾張<br />\n影完就交換幫我哋影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da24364fc808b0c4737aba01013f335ddb152d2b","tid":2231347,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"返緊份酒吧工 瑞士鬼婆點歌 佢比隊名我 之後我播咗幾首歌 佢開心到 叫我幫佢同佢個佬影相 又錫我左邊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呆咗幾秒 當時19歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜有瑞士佬同行 唔係嗰晚ez <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bec55f50ff9321bf5e1a42506f43b74e70d660","tid":2231347,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"雖然好無聊，但係支持有圖開post"}]}